</p>, <p>概率模型的主要任務就集中在估計<span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math alttext="{\displaystyle P(D|R)}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
